Use effect hooks-
________________________________________-

Updating document title to the current counter value

We need the code in 2 places-


componentDidMount(){
document.title = {this.state.count}
}

componentDidUpdate(){
document.title = {this.state.count}
}

And we want to remove the title on componentWillUnmount

 componentWillUnmount(){
Remove the code
}


Duplication of code is there.

________________________

useEffect- The use effect hook let us perform the side effects in functional components,

 it is close replacement for componentDidMount, componentWillUpdate and componentWillUnmount.








